'''Samantha Mugatsia''' (wavutse 1992) ni umukinnyi w'amafirime muri [[Kenya]].

== Ubuzima bwa Biografiya ==
Mugatsia yavutse mu 1992, umukobwa wa Grace Gitau. Yakuriye i [[Nairobi]] kandi akora nk'ingoma y'itsinda The Machine Machine. <ref name="mangat" /> Yari yaranakoze akazi ko kwerekana imideli. <ref>https://www.jeuneafrique.com/mag/559384/culture/cinema-rafiki-amour-et-censure-a-nairobi/</ref> Mugatsia yize amategeko muri Kaminuza Gatolika yo muri [[Afurika]] y'Iburasirazuba ariko ahagarika amasomo ye kugira ngo atangire umwuga we wo gukina. Mu Gushyingo 2016, yari yitabiriye pop-in y'abahanzi ubwo yamenyanwaga n'umuyobozi wa firime Wanuri Kahiu, amubwira ko yanditse inyandiko kandi ashaka kwerekana Mugatsia. Nubwo atigeze akora, Mugatsia yemeye uruhare. 

Muri 2018, Mugatsia yakinnye na Kena Mwaura, umwe mu bantu babiri bakomeye, muri ''[[Rafiki]]'' ya Kahiu. Iyi nkuru ishingiye ku gitabo cyitwa ''Jambula Igiti'' cyanditswe n'umwanditsi wa Uganda Monica Arac de Nyeko kandi kirasobanura urukundo ruteye imbere hagati y’abakobwa babiri aho bibujijwe kuryamana kw'abahuje igitsina. Mu rwego rwo kwitegura uruhare, Mugatsia yafashe amezi menshi yamasomo yo gukina kandi yitoza gukoresha imyitozo yindorerwamo no kubaho mubitekerezo.  Iyi filime yari itemewe muri Kenya, aho kuryamana kw'abahuje igitsina bitemewe. ''Rafiki'' abaye film ya mbere yo muri Kenya yerekanwe mu Iserukiramuco rya sinema i Cannes . <ref>https://www.houstonchronicle.com/entertainment/movies_tv/article/Kenyan-gay-life-comes-into-focus-in-Rafiki-13829398.php</ref> Ann Hornaday wo muri Washington Post yise imikorere ya Mugatsia "yitonze." <ref>https://www.washingtonpost.com/goingoutguide/movies/movie-about-teenage-girls-in-love-is-a-breakthrough-for-kenyan-filmmaker/2019/05/06/a910b1e4-6c5d-11e9-be3a-33217240a539_story.html</ref> Mugatsia yatsindiye igihembo cy'umukinnyi witwaye neza mu iserukiramuco rya FESPACO rya 2019 ryabereye i Ouagadougou, Burkina Faso kubera kwerekana Kena. <ref>https://www.cnn.com/2019/03/04/africa/banned-lesbian-movie-wins-award-intl/index.html</ref> Ihagarikwa rya filime ryakuweho nyuma gato yuko Kahiu atanga ikirego, kugira ngo yerekane muri Kenya kugira ngo yemererwe guhabwa ibihembo bya Academy. <ref>https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-47435329</ref>

Mugatsia yerekana ko ari iby'umwuka. Yanze kugira icyo atangaza ku mibonano mpuzabitsina ye, ariko agirira impuhwe umuryango wa LGBT. 

